videos.description: Devwah Whaley runs the ball 5 yards for a touchdown to put Arkansas in the lead 7-0.
videos.headline: Whaley runs it 5 yds for a TD

videos.description: Arkansas coach Bret Bielema recaps what the Razorbacks did well on defense and what needs to be adjusted for the next half.
videos.headline: Bielema highlights defensive adjustments for the second half

videos.description: Hans Supre fumbles the ball and Henre Toliver recovers, then returns it 18 yards for a touchdown to extend Arkansas' lead to 28-0.
videos.headline: Toliver returns fumble to the house for Arkansas TD

videos.description: Chase Hayden stretches out for a touchdown to give Arkansas a 35-0 lead.
videos.headline: Hayden stretches out for a 5-yard TD
